Metadata.Title: Dual Agent Status
Metadata.Description: 47,The Board has given us a new special assignment that may benefit the ICA in the future.  The agency is experimenting with sending multiple agents into the field at the same time.The first test will be sending two agents on a mission to gather data on how efficient our operations will be.This, of course, means that we will need multiple safehouses for our agents, so that we do not draw any suspicion to ourselves.Secure a second safe house for our first experiment.  Good luck, 47.
